{"tid":783974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【月光族】身光頸靚指揮家戶口低見四位數 女友：佢唔開源唔節流佛系儲錢","createTime":"2018-08-18T04:06:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T09:28:12.000Z","uid":28765,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a6450e9b5879f2abf7eabe2b02ede23a57e1f3f2","tid":783974,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"年初，香港教育大學教育政策與領導學系做了個調查， 指香港年輕一代中，10個有6個係月光族；另一邊，金融科技初創企業Gini於去年12月，訪問了500位80後、90後，有3成受訪者「唔知啲錢使咗喺邊」。在這人工唔加，衣食住行乜都加；樓價點都追唔到，遠大目標遠到車尾燈都望唔到的年代，不如活在當下，月光，好奇咩？　<br />\n<br />\n「好多人說我是月光族，其實我都唔係好光啫。」30歲的楊帆（Stanley）是個音樂家，演奏會指揮、中提琴樂手、鋼琴老師──通通都是他。facebook上的他一身「踢死兔」，於演奏廳指揮管弦樂團，無論點睇都係中產才子；但眼前一身<br />\nT shirt短褲、坐在地下打機的他，卻說自己只是一位收入不穩的Slasher。接受訪問時，他於銀行有3萬港元存款，原來已是歷年高位，有時則跌剩4位數字。嗯，一額汗。我知喇，佢一定成日食好着好，養車去旅行，兼洗腳唔抹腳啦！咦，但係佢每日平均工時只有兩個半鐘咋喎，吓？<br />\n其中一個身份是鋼琴老師的他這樣答我﹕「閒日大家都只係夜晚先練琴嘛，想搵多啲錢都冇。我在家就多花時間練琴、看書同學外語。星期日最多生意，但我好衰，想留來陪女友（笑），咁搵錢都係為生活啫，我哋得周日相處，如果咁都冇埋，唔得喎！」<br />\n以目前樓價市況，二人絕不考慮買樓，「根本講難聽啲係黐X線的，我打個比喻，就好似用成千蚊食碟叉飯咁。」早年他住沙頭角，700呎村屋連天台，包埋免費泊車位先7,500港元，閒時開車去郊野公園、海灘，勁舒爽；後來搬回大埔，佢第一件事就是賣車，「乜都加，呢幾年去茶餐廳食飯，都起碼加咗3成啦，屋租又唔同晒！單是泊車位都要二、三千元一個月，原來郊遊一次的油費好貴，加埋爆胎、壞車同保險。索性唔開車就省好多了。」<br />\n<br />\n醉心音樂　歐洲進修每次5萬<br />\n咁，啲錢去咗邊呢？他拿出厚厚一本Cert，「我見到啲歐洲演奏大師班，忍唔住又去報。為期一星期的課程，動輒二、三萬元。」嘩，噴血，但Stanley個表情興奮得有點像sales，「但佢有成隊專業交響樂團任你耍喎！加埋機票、酒店，再喺嗰邊玩多幾日，去一次都要5萬蚊。最癲係16同17年，去咗4次呀！」幾年的積蓄，化成桌上一大叠英國音樂學院畢業證書、大師班證書，總值起碼200萬。財散人安樂，人到三張，朋友有車有樓，他卻無所謂地說﹕「我有好多張Cert啊！」<br />\n這時女友Ida話，「佢係佛系儲錢，即不開源，不節流，錢自然會儲到。」全屋爆笑。「我識佢時，已知音樂家收入不穩，他有時到歐洲比賽都有成本；但你不進修、不比賽又會踎墩，仲衰啊！所以『月光』都有原因；而且我的安全感，從不來自男友有幾多錢，我就是我自己的安全感。」現時二人夾份租屋，生活費則平分。放假在家打機，拖手逛公園海旁，又或搭一程巴士去新娘潭，生活一樣梳干，「我們想做的事，都不必花大錢，不想買樓，婚禮不要大龍鳳，簡簡單單就好。」<br />\n今年Stanley踏入29+1，與此同時，他與音樂朋友們開始接現場演奏的工作，為婚禮、活動及微電影等創作專屬配樂或主題曲。此為開源也。有了目標，儲錢就有了根基，「以前儲到十萬好開心，但因為冇目標，使使吓又冇咗，而家易儲好多。」不過剛才我收到Stanley訊息，「我報了個比賽，成功出線，意味着我的戶口又要重入月光境界了。」<br />\n記者：陳慧敏<br />\n攝影：伍慶泉、許先煜　<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180816/large/1534417422_eaf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180816%2Flarge%2F1534417422_eaf3.jpg&h=ec034082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStanley要對所有樂器及曲譜有一定認識，才可勝任指揮一職，所以要不停上課進修。　<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180816/large/1534417422_01df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180816%2Flarge%2F1534417422_01df.jpg&h=6fce6288&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他於英國皇家音樂學院修讀四年，畢業時百多萬埋單，打後每年到歐洲進修，儲來一本厚厚「證書冊」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180816/large/1534417421_65a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180816%2Flarge%2F1534417421_65a1.jpg&h=262edbef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以為賣掉愛車會不慣，但搭巴士的日子都好方便，Ida笑說：「仲有埋司機，去邊都唔使煩啊！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180818/58571891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F58571891&d=Jjntxr48oCGt5aGYjZmvnwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=95051ce4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180818%2F58571891&h=b09aefba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180818/58571891</a>"},{"pid":"209258ab3abec55caf4e0ec84a6fea642fa24535","tid":783974,"uid":198622,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adcd28d950c8f6af935d652cd3e86f61cdc9f8e7","tid":783974,"uid":139228,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"現實中既千秋"},{"pid":"4542a13987e33fc03ad3e08a48e6887cb25859ae","tid":783974,"uid":140454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:13:38.000Z","msg":"其實拎錢進修唔算開源既一種？"},{"pid":"aef828354e8bbaea656b60778b40b914adf1f4cd","tid":783974,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"去上下理財班"},{"pid":"81a06a1443af2ff67b5dc0a803cf80a52cfcc03d","tid":783974,"uid":121409,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"真係有夢想有能力嘅，用啲錢嚟做自己鍾意又做得好嘅事，好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有儲錢反而唔知儲嚟為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008642aa57ce7452c3f198f8423a27096884cbd1","tid":783974,"uid":152209,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"平身條友就好有錢 仲好搵得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f71b14129c9f39a199ed5143dacc6ca7559fc4","tid":783974,"uid":32699,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"佢唔係亂洗錢吃喝玩樂玩名牌 某程度都叫為自己事業發展 幾好吖"},{"pid":"5ebbd2828b80881353abccfb508259ddf62da7a7","tid":783974,"uid":39329,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"最respect就係依啲人"},{"pid":"973e76d044757562010a361d98078962b5fd2799","tid":783974,"uid":5700,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"有能力嘅人搵錢唔會難，月光只係佢個人選擇，其實佢想搵返正常收入都得"},{"pid":"83a02b741d04664896fe3d74d4148a62efd6eb03","tid":783974,"uid":86418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:29:38.000Z","msg":"搵得番, 唔怕洗"},{"pid":"ca222b8855fa414e5187b1498a0788ebc553494f","tid":783974,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc0944cbeb3069a0cd5bcf976b122b8843bde6ee","tid":783974,"uid":54142,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"ca222b8855fa414e5187b1498a0788ebc553494f","tid":783974,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:33:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"人地都叫做把錢花在事業上<br />\n係香港先咁ON9 連人才都容納唔到"},{"pid":"d0792233c0fa39bf2657da4f50e2d0c5cbe63056","tid":783974,"uid":2300,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"佢要搵番錢唔難<br />\n<br />\n佢去個d 所謂旅遊既洗費唔係淨係出，而係真係學野同有張cert 啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點同大部份港豬淨係得張boarding pass 同激安既退稅單"},{"pid":"2b257ad3221188d256fa42ecddf0eeace5c6d157","tid":783974,"uid":77277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"佢咪之前上過星期日檔案講拍拖姊弟戀果pair"},{"pid":"9396c317cc67153b74c7365eb5953f621bcf10f6","tid":783974,"uid":64948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"佢起碼將d錢用係裝備自己，都係一件好事來"},{"pid":"643f28faa3600150f0f49debc58040b59aefa94a","tid":783974,"uid":198622,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:27:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"624dab607c2d8cfb046754776a0705eb76ce0241","tid":783974,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209258ab3abec55caf4e0ec84a6fea642fa24535","tid":783974,"uid":198622,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"啲港女 會話你唔上進架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d55bca7cc873e0fd94e50f770792d000b0a7a4f","tid":783974,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"624dab607c2d8cfb046754776a0705eb76ce0241","tid":783974,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209258ab3abec55caf4e0ec84a6fea642fa24535","tid":783974,"uid":198622,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:28:45.000Z","msg":"啲港女 會話你唔上進架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"港女: 冇樓即係冇上進心"},{"pid":"91fb420474b23d3c4c3977821e74e73b0b2cc384","tid":783974,"uid":11417,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:54:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e67f69f366cd837962eb5d02cd2dee55fc46fce","tid":783974,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:57:27.000Z","msg":"課金都課5000啦"},{"pid":"d66b985789db2721917af422e117334607b1c4b0","tid":783974,"uid":126648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"一日做兩粒鐘<br />\n又有女屌 肯夾份租樓<br />\n<br />\n仲有咁多錢進修<br />\n根本係人生贏家"},{"pid":"3ae836f777f2be776ccd0900bbeb0ab3ce386f6e","tid":783974,"uid":109560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"呢啲人既人生先係人生<br />\n每日都做自己鍾意做既事"},{"pid":"bb8e3d35137eacd41d516317a63951dcca355cd4","tid":783974,"uid":99546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"攞哂去嫖賭飲就話姐 <br />\n佢洗咁多有CERT 都算係增值自己 又同自己事業有關 冇問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4227aa34aaf82b9ca238a5c3bc35fca8564e99","tid":783974,"uid":60136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb8e3d35137eacd41d516317a63951dcca355cd4","tid":783974,"uid":99546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T06:15:17.000Z","msg":"攞哂去嫖賭飲就話姐 <br />\n佢洗咁多有CERT 都算係增值自己 又同自己事業有關 冇問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"所以港女所謂既上進心同安全感 都係一場笑話 講到尾就係要增加資源再洗喺佢地身上 加唔可以投訴 唔可以反駁"}]}